data.title: Minister of Transport and Communications (Finland)
data.meta_description: The Minister of Transport and Communications is one of the Finnish Government's ministerial positions. The Minister of Transport and Communications heads the Ministry of Transport and Communications.
data.text:
The Minister of Transport and Communications (Finnish: liikenne- ja viestint√§ministeri, Swedish: kommunikationsminister) is one of the Finnish Government's ministerial positions.[1] The Minister of Transport and Communications heads the Ministry of Transport and Communications.

The incumbent holder of the position is Lulu Ranne of the Finns Party.
